name: Sword Art Online (+ Alicization) Anime Style LoRA
description:
Sword Art Online (+ Alicization) Anime style LoRA

Check both version tabs

Making models can be expensive. Do you like what I do? Consider supporting me on Patreon 🅿️, feel free to buy me a coffee ☕ or just leave a ❤️


This style was requested a lot, but this anime changes a lot between each season, especially from season 1 to Alicization. I decided to make both as two separate models.

Works perfectly on AnyLoRA at weight 1. Increase the accuracy with the trigger sao anime style for the 1st season LoRA, and alicization anime style for the Alicization season LoRA. Also keep in mind your LoRA file name might be different from the ones I used in examples.

(Remember this is a style lora, so while it can probably make similar characters from the game, it might not be super accurate without a character lora. See the examples)


How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight according to the instructions (by default it's :1)
